87bd0f0347f2d7ef480a73b6c2915d4da0879815c77e8e2a236edff95ddd571b956625f7adc7cde995ceca46bf4b93ed92e6dac94f90195f832066baf6c1f616  0001-Fix-inline-functions-to-use-static-inline.patch"
